    <p>
    <b> 29.h3? </b>(White <i class="cleanuphtml-1">must</i> defend the g2 pawn instead)<b>, Bxg2+; 30.Kh2 </b>(Kg1 is no better)<b>, Nf3+ </b>(Wins the exchange)<b>; 31.Kg3, Nxh4; 32.Rc8+, Bf8;
      33.Kxh4 </b>(33.Bh6 threatening mate at f8 doesn't work because of 33...., Nf5+)<b>, Kg7; 34.Nd7, Be7+; 35.Kg3, d2 </b>(wins more material)<b>; 36.Be5+? </b>(White <i><span class=
